I dont understand how I'm suppose to Compile those Files without the compiler being in that folder, but if I go back to the Bin, Data, deps , src, run, compile and compile there, restart server and I see no Changes can somebody please track me on the right road, I got no idea what I'm doing, and also can somebody link me to a good PI Source+Client.
